Under the tutelage of Wu, Monks are able to hone their skills to the point of being able to execute a second and sometimes even third strike when scoring a hit with their special attacks. This ability grants a ten percent increase in the chance of scoring multiple special attacks, per rank.<br>
MNK - (10% * X ranks)<br>
<br>
<br>
anyone else notice that is says a &quot;ten percent increase in the chance of scoring multiple special attacks&quot; <br>
<br>
but what chance is it increasing?  Its possible that levels 61-65 may on their own add &quot;combo&quot; attacks and this simply augments that. <br>
<br>
although I think its more likely that this AA skill is the only way to combo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uapoccih.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Apoc CiH</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/30/02 11:37:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32341.topic&index=63>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.comedycentral.com/dailyshow/images/lewisrace.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AXP abilities for PoP</span><hr size=1> It seems like this was supposed to be a 3 or 5 tier skill that they changed to a 1 time dragon punch type thing for 5 points. My guess would be it's a 10% chance to attempt a second flying kick if the first lands and a 10% chance to do a third if the second lands. Increase in DPS from this would be far less than even Combat Fury so I hope it's a little more interesting but that's my guess. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessageRange?topicID=32341.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessageRange?topicID=32341.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessageRange?topicID=32341.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=32341.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showNextMessage?topicID=32341.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3234